5. Demonstrate the usage of tapply function in R 
CODE: 
data <- data.frame(a = c(3, 4, 1),b = c(6, 2, 3),c = c(5,8,10)) 
print(data) 
print(tapply(data$c,data$a,mean)) 
OUTPUT: 
a b c 
