Exercise 3 
Create two data frame df1 and df2: 
> df1 
Id Age 
1 1 14 
2 2 12 
3 3 15 
4 4 10 
> df2 
Id Sex Code 
1 1 F a 
2 2 M b 
3 3 M c 
4 4 F d 
From df1 and df2 create M: 
>M 
Id Age Sex Code 
1 1 14 F a 
2 2 12 M b 
3 3 15 M c 4 4 10 F d
8 
CODE: 
id=c(1:4) 
age=c(14,12,15,10) 
sex=c("F","M","M","F") 
code=c("a","b","c","d") 
df1=data.frame(id,age) 
df2=data.frame(id,sex,code) 
df3=merge(df1,df2) 
print(df3) 
