corresponding variables. 
CODE: 
buildings= data.frame(location=c(1, 2, 3), name=c("building1", "building2","building3")) 
data=data.frame(survey=c(1,1,1,2,2,2),location=c(1,2,3,2,3,1),efficiency=c(51,64,70,7,80,58)
) 
